title: [Orzel's General Store]
[Orzel's Magic Shoppe]
description: A midnight blue rising phoenix tapestry hangs on one of the plain wooden walls, and a vaulted ceiling rises overhead.  A brass flowerpot sits in one corner of a dark-stained oak floor.  There is an engraved copper bin on one side of the shop and a vine-carved mahogany table on the other.
